        "evidence": "<p>RTS = (0.9368*GCS Value) + (0.7326*SBP Value) + (0.2908*RR Value)</p>",
        "facts": "<p>See Formula Table below:</p>\n<div class=\"table-responsive\">\n<table class=\"table table-bordered table-hover\">\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>Numerical Value Assigned</th>\n<th>Glasgow Coma Scale</th>\n<th>Systolic Blood Pressure</th>\n<th>Respiratory Rate</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>4</strong></td>\n<td>13-15</td>\n<td>&gt;89</td>\n<td>10-29</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>3</strong></td>\n<td>9-12</td>\n<td>76-89</td>\n<td>&gt;29</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>2</strong></td>\n<td>6-8</td>\n<td>50-75</td>\n<td>6-9</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>1</strong></td>\n<td>4-5</td>\n<td>1-49</td>\n<td>1-5</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>0</strong></td>\n<td>3</td>\n<td>0</td>\n<td>0</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n</div>",
